data.meta_description: Princess Margaret Louise of Prussia Duchess of Connaught. Self: Path√©'s Weekly, No. 45. Princess Margaret Louise of Prussia Duchess of Connaught was born on 25 July 1860 in Potsdam, Kingdom of Prussia [now Brandenburg, Germany]. She was married to Prince Arthur Duke of Connaught. She died on 14 March 1917 in Westminster, London, England, UK.
